name: COZY ROOM 02
description:
[COZY ROOM COLLECTION - PREMIUM]

I pour my messages for the world onto pieces of paper with my favorite typewriter, ink, and quill while I sit in a warm and cozy room as snow falls gracefully outside my window. Candles and heater dim and glow in this room and it forms shadows that dance to music that I listen to. 

Original art and animation by 196 Pixels Light
Music by LuxirusVein
